metadata.description:
Review of the Cortical Circuit with regards to object behavior. Reviewing the key idea and brainstorming about open questions.

00:00 Introduction to Movement Vectors and Features
01:22 Review of Previous Work and New Theories
51:34 Exploring the Complexity of Saxophone Recognition
56:32 Challenges in Representing Complex Features
01:42:22 The Puzzle Analogy and Scientific Challenges
02:27:30 Understanding Predictive Models and Sensory Input
02:34:30 Challenges in Behavioral and Morphological Predictions
